the heart.

16:47.924 --> 16:49.130
HOUSE:
Blah, blah, blah, blah.

16:49.217 --> 16:50.878
Who cares about
the medical mumbo-jumbo?

16:50.968 --> 16:52.003
Tell him the treatment.

16:52.094 --> 16:55.222
Well, it's complicated.

16:55.306 --> 16:56.466
