Nabasynth.

17:02.230 --> 17:06.223
Yes. So all we
have to do now is
write a prescription

17:06.317 --> 17:08.774
and have him
pick up the pills.

17:14.158 --> 17:15.534
(CHUCKLES)

17:16.702 --> 17:18.078
That's it?

17:19.247 --> 17:20.862
I take some pills,
I'm gonna be okay?

17:20.957 --> 17:25.200
The real tragedy here
is that the Tiburon swab
technology didn't exist

17:25.294 --> 17:28.001
to detect Ortoli
back in your dad's day.

17:30.800 --> 17:32.586
He could have lived?

17:35.471 --> 17:36.677
(SlGHS)

17:37.515 --> 17:38.880
